From 34cbc55c64eadf07cded1c998f674be4f1fef144 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 12:00:41 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] asmjit: add OH GN BUILD and bundle.json

Register asmjit as an OH 'thirdparty' subsystem component with two targets: libasmjit (shared, runtime) and libasmjit_frontend_static. Public config exports the diagnostic pragmas and -I src so consumers compile cleanly. Listed last on purpose in arkencoder_config: GN appends config cflags in order, and the -Wno-bitwise-instead-of-logical / -Wno-unused-but-set-variable / -Wno-deprecated-copy here must come after ark_config's -Wall to win.

Signed-off-by: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
---
 BUILD.gn    | 171 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 bundle.json |  43 +++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 214 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 BUILD.gn
 create mode 100644 bundle.json

diff --git a/BUILD.gn b/BUILD.gn
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..744d48d
--- /dev/null
+++ b/BUILD.gn
@@ -0,0 +1,171 @@
